    "content": "<p>A ceiling fan is rotating around a fixed axle as shown. The direction of angular velocity is along .......... .</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1m5w52jto/5f793791-5dd2-47be-b0af-09e9bdc4cbd5/65da21c0-d247-11ef-80d9-bd33a9c6e008/file-jaoe38c1m5w52jtp.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1m5w52jto/5f793791-5dd2-47be-b0af-09e9bdc4cbd5/65da21c0-d247-11ef-80d9-bd33a9c6e008/file-jaoe38c1m5w52jtp.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"KCET 2024 Physics - Rotational Motion Question 4 English\"></p>",
